{"tid":732002,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[冠聯尾班車]游蕙禎 對 梁嘉琪--2017-18 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附加賽決賽","createTime":"2018-07-06T16:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T14:00:24.000Z","uid":92376,"like":68,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16cc7dc5046818dafe24b53a9c62e46029a95b2e","tid":732002,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎v梁嘉琪<br />\n<br />\n甲組全季積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/umnriTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FumnriTu.png&h=487bdb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附加賽決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-7-7 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/t8X8RMa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ft8X8RMa.png&h=66a3de83&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CdGYLFC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCdGYLFC.png&h=d43fcfa5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(9)游蕙禎vs梁嘉琪(8)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"5153df2b01e69770133a8d8e9aa01b3b36502aba","tid":732002,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"今場勝方將會升上下季港冠"},{"pid":"df898292341b64e6d3d06c927637f4a0e333bc7e","tid"